{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/vorpaljs/awesome-vorpal/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"fbf093e2-bccf-5285-9e60-f7da46f1fe44","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-vorpal-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-vorpal-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome vorpal awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome Vorpal <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<p>A curated list of delightful <a href=\"https://github.com/dthree/vorpal\">Vorpal</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dthree/vorpal\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">5.4k</span></span></a>-based projects and extensions.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/dthree/vorpal\">Vorpal is Node's first framework for building immersive CLI applications.</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dthree/vorpal\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">5.4k</span></span></a></p>\n<p>Inspired by the <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\">awesome</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">164.8k</span></span></a> list thing.</p>\n<h2 id=\"table-of-contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#table-of-contents\" aria-label=\"table of contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Table of Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#community\">Community</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tutorials\">Tutorials</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#projects\">Projects</a></