 you through developing a sophisticated Vorpal app from scratch.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"http://daily-javascript.com/articles/vorpal/\">By Ramon Gebben</a></p>\n<p>A brief introduction to Vorpal by the author of <a href=\"https://github.com/vorpaljs/awesome-vorpal/blob/master/daily-javascript.com\">daily-javascript.com</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"projects\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#projects\" aria-label=\"projects permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Projects</h2>\n<p><em>Awesome projects and applications built using Vorpal.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dthree/cash\">Cash</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dthree/cash\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">7.7k</span></span></a> - Cross-platform Linux commands without the suck.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/Firefox_OS/Automated_testing/Raptor\">Raptor</a> - Performance testing CLI for Firefox developers.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mischah/itunes-remote/\">iTunes-remote</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mischah/itunes-remote/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">409</span></span></a> - Control iTunes on the CLI.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Kristories/phunt\">phunt</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Kristories/phunt\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">106</span></span></a> - Access <a href=\"https://www.producthunt.com/\">Product Hunt</a> on the CLI. <em>Trended on (you guessed it) Product Hunt.</em></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/websitesfortrello/trelew\">trelew</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/websitesfortrello/trelew\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">85</span></span></a> - Access <a href=\"https://trello.com/\">Trello</a> on the CLI.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dthree/wat\">wat</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dthree/wat\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">448</span></span></a> - Community-built docs for every language, platform and library.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/AljoschaMeyer/metronome-cli\">metronome</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/AljoschaMeyer/metronome-cli\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">8</span></span></a> - A live metronome on the CLI.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/fastack/cli\">fastack</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/fastack/cli\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;bord